<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_d3a7e188-6991-4593-88ae-78c180b47f43" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>C2P5</sptc><title id="_32b42fc7-ed6e-4ab8-828e-c137196b388d">Contamination</title><archive-num>2019:CP2.1</archive-num><subclause id="_f70cf85e-db27-4a45-9434-067b94e3cf17" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_2bde93c9-f94d-4046-b6bf-8678d09b2792">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The entry of water, foul gases, sewerage and sullage from a sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9440_0.8.0.xml#_8310df67-b7b9-4f62-b022-0655a2ae4428" id="_dccfd32c-b81b-4765-86c5-dc8fa84f8590" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drainage system</xref> into buildings must be avoided.</p></subclause><subclause id="_e2f04ecd-aca9-433d-bd80-943c6f20124d" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_01566d73-78d8-4a30-a370-32b0fa570ea9">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9440_0.8.0.xml#_8310df67-b7b9-4f62-b022-0655a2ae4428" id="_d6b52d6c-9fe7-4764-b90b-901be76fb164" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drainage system</xref> must be protected against internal contamination.</p></subclause><subclause id="_586594c6-27c9-45b9-b776-1b60607259d4" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_a47eba2e-688a-4211-8e73-9a6ff61ddb46">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>The entry of foul gases from a sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9440_0.8.0.xml#_8310df67-b7b9-4f62-b022-0655a2ae4428" id="_c45b330a-4bef-4d49-8181-47b9867cf485" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drainage system</xref> into buildings must be avoided, such that—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_409a3354-5706-4188-ab87-de02d671b907">at pressures of up to ±375 Pa, water trap seals will not be reduced to depths less than—<ol><li>70 mm for trap seals in pressurised rooms; and</li><li>25 mm for all other applications; or</li></ol></li><li id="_60b8175a-570e-48b3-96ba-31ac5f04e563">an equivalent level of safety to human health is achieved as a system complying to (a).</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_7973e5fb-0c1f-48c1-becc-a2d170020b10" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_f79c60a1-3d14-4872-b7d1-e740481f543e">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>The entry of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1486_26.7.0.xml#_02c3900f-c9bb-470b-93f4-d71555f2fea7" id="_df0c4758-0d6e-4d06-a7ee-7c4916952459" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">surface water</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9502_0.6.0.xml#_49fcb971-d792-44ac-af74-6243aa2b5b23" id="_279f1e81-aeaf-4b1a-9524-374a1078249b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">sub-surface water</xref> and stormwater into a sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9440_0.8.0.xml#_8310df67-b7b9-4f62-b022-0655a2ae4428" id="_dd094cee-3f55-4338-88a6-3a106435f586" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drainage system</xref> must be avoided.</p></subclause><callout id="_106f1c9f-e785-4d47-9875-081c2cb99ad4"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>Consideration should be given to the type, quality and quantity of waste being discharged to a sanitary <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/9440_0.8.0.xml#_8310df67-b7b9-4f62-b022-0655a2ae4428" id="_dbe761e1-5789-4b01-bd7a-f6047033c950" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drainage system</xref> and the suitability and compatibility of the materials used.</p></callout></clause>